machine_end_gcode:
G91 ;Relative positioning
G1 Z5 F720 ;Raise Z
G1 E-5 F300 ;Retract a bit to protect nozzle
M104 S0 ;Turn off extruder
M140 S0 ;Turn off bed
M107 ;Turn off all fans
G90 ;Absolute positioning
G1 X200 Y200 F4800 ;Parking the hotend
M84 X Y E ;All steppers off but left Z
machine_start_gcode:
G90 ; use absolute positioning
M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer] ; set bed temperature
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer] ; wait for bed to reach target temperature
G28 ; home all axes (without mesh bed leveling)
G29 ; perform mesh bed leveling
M104 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; set nozzle temperature (without waiting)
G92 E0.0 ; reset extruder position
G1 Y-2.0 X150 F2400 ; move to intro line start position
G1 Z3 F720 ; lift Z axis slightly
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; wait for nozzle to reach target temperature
G1 X150 F1000 ; move quickly to start of line
G1 Z0.2 F720 ; lower Z axis to printing height
G1 X80.0 E8.0 F900 ; extrude first part of intro line
G1 X20.0 E10.0 F700 ; extrude second part of intro line
G92 E0.0 ; reset extruder position
name: fdm_machine_eryone_ER20_common
